node.text:
FIRST Bass Nation Tournament of the season!🎣 
St. John’s River was tough, we learned from our mistakes the first day and picked it up a little the second day. I’m thankful that the Lord gives us a new day full of new opportunities. It was tons of fun figuring out these stubborn fish, can’t wait for the next stop in Harris Chain (October 2nd-3rd)!!! 
• 
Y’all go follow @rafesexton_fishing !! He VALID✅ 
#bassfishing #bassnation #tournamentseason #fishingtrip #palatkaflorida #stjohnsriver #youtube #newvideosoon #largemouthbass #fishing #bass

node.text:
Y’all help me wish my beautiful, hard working, loving, supportive, God fearing momma a HAPPY BIRTHDAYYYY!!!🥳 @suzanne_martin 
•
Mom, I can’t explain how blessed I am to call you my mother/best friend all in one! You go above and beyond ALWAYS for us and you have sacrificed so much keeping this family put together. We would have no idea what to do without you, you’re the glue to this family!❤️ Your love for Christ showed me who I need to be as a Christian and you’re the best example I could ever get to just be who I am. You’re so supportive in everything that I do and you give the best advice! I’ve never gone wrong when I listen to you, but what can I say “Mom’s always know best” ;) Anyway to wrap this up, I love you more than anything on the face of this earth and beyond that. You’re my rock momma and I can’t thank God enough for putting you as my best friend/mother all in one in my life❤️ 
#mommasgirl #birthdaygirl #mybestfriend #dasue #happybirthdaymom #ilovemomma #Godisgood #momsarethebest #momsbestfriend #daughterlove #mommyslove
